{
  "stem": "6878.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, we start-- and 10 days later, I got a job with a Russian unit, a military unit, and because of my language, Russian, and writing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was-- they appointed me to be the manager of stores, big stores.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had some stores, goods, which they schlepped from Germany out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it wasn't so much when I started, but then they filled up as time-- they filled it-- they schlep it out from Germany, all the goods.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we lived first class.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We started to live a normal life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Me being the manager of the stores, we had everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had food, plenty, and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We used to-- when we used to eat meat, we used to lock the door that nobody can sometimes go in and see that we eating meat and so on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's why everything was a luxury.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then it started to come in groups.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Like, for example, it came in, 50 cases of, pane glass, glass.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when Kovno was bombed, the glass was like gold.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I reported this to the officer in charge, that 50 cases of glass came in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he just-- he says to me, it's 45.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to him, [SPEAKING RUSSIAN] It's pretty set.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's 50.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, don't be an idiot, in Russian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't be a-- don't be a [RUSSIAN], an idiot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Five cases fell off the truck, and I'll give you tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you go and sell them tomorrow on the black market, and I'll give you tomorrow a note.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So tomorrow, yes, I go out, and I knew Kovno well because I was working there before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I sold them, and I bring 25,000 rubles for the glass.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
